==Trivia==
*In the comics, Pepper Potts married [[Happy Hogan]] twice.
*Potts' favorite drink is a dry olive martini.{{Ref|IM}}{{Ref|IM2DS}}
*She is allergic to strawberries.{{Ref|IM2}}
*Potts was responsible for curating [[Tony Stark]]'s art collection as his assistant for over a decade.{{Ref|IM2}}
*Potts was featured in ''[[Forbes]]'' with the headline "Pepper Potts Stirs Up Stark."{{Ref|IM3}}

